### Create Barber
POST http://localhost:8080/api/barbers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Mike",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "mike@barbershop.com",
  "phone": "0871234568",
  "password": "password123",
  "bio": "10 years experience in fades and beard styling",
  "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/photos/mike.jpg"
}

### Get All Barbers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/barbers

### Get Active Barbers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/barbers/active

### Get Barber by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/barbers/1

### Update Barber
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/barbers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bio": "15 years experience specializing in modern fades",
  "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/photos/mike-updated.jpg"
}

### Deactivate Barber
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/barbers/1/deactivate

### Delete Barber
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/barbers/1